1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,780
=Episode 7=

3
00:00:58,240 --> 00:00:59,880
(I don't understand.)

4
00:00:59,880 --> 00:01:02,399
(First, he took a severe wound for me)

5
00:01:02,399 --> 00:01:04,359
(just so I could perform
before the court)

6
00:01:04,359 --> 00:01:05,959
(and catch the Emperor's eye.)

7
00:01:06,719 --> 00:01:09,200
(Then, he risked offending His Majesty)

8
00:01:09,200 --> 00:01:11,439
(to rescue me
from the Palace of Punishment.)

9
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:14,560
(It's contradictory.)

10
00:01:22,319 --> 00:01:24,519
(It seems you're just like me,)

11
00:01:25,159 --> 00:01:27,079
(trapped in this cage,)

12
00:01:27,079 --> 00:01:28,599
(with no control over your own fate.)

13
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:47,840
(How boring.)

14
00:02:03,439 --> 00:02:05,120
(Compared to being forgotten,)

15
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:06,799
(isolated,)

16
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:08,240
(and abandoned,)

17
00:02:09,159 --> 00:02:11,599
(what is physical pain?)

18
00:02:11,800 --> 00:02:12,960
(I know)

19
00:02:13,319 --> 00:02:15,240
(you want them dead.)

20
00:02:28,439 --> 00:02:30,360
Your Majesty must be tired.

21
00:02:31,319 --> 00:02:32,639
Have something to eat.

22
00:02:32,639 --> 00:02:33,759
I have no appetite.

23
00:02:36,199 --> 00:02:37,439
I know

24
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:39,240
what Your Majesty wants.

25
00:02:42,039 --> 00:02:43,919
I promise you,

26
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:46,759
whether it was Jiang Yusang before

27
00:02:47,319 --> 00:02:49,479
or Jiang Yukui now,

28
00:02:50,159 --> 00:02:51,919
alive or dead,

29
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:53,800
they will both be yours.

30
00:02:53,800 --> 00:02:55,919
My mind is on another woman.

31
00:02:55,919 --> 00:02:57,960
You truly don't mind?

32
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:59,680
Didn't you want to be

33
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:01,919
my one and only?

34
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:05,680
If your view is narrow,

35
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:08,199
your heart can hold only one.

36
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:09,639
You are the Emperor.

37
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,360
All under heaven

38
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,879
belongs to you.

39
00:03:13,639 --> 00:03:14,639
Those women

40
00:03:14,639 --> 00:03:16,080
are nothing more

41
00:03:16,319 --> 00:03:18,120
than playthings in your palm,

42
00:03:18,560 --> 00:03:20,479
easily obtained.

43
00:03:20,479 --> 00:03:23,280
Rather than be the only one
in your heart,

44
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:25,719
I'd rather be the one
you care about most.

45
00:03:26,039 --> 00:03:27,159
Your Majesty,

46
00:03:27,159 --> 00:03:28,680
am I the one?

47
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:33,719
(Leave!)

48
00:03:33,719 --> 00:03:34,560
(Just go!)

49
00:03:35,080 --> 00:03:36,560
(Am I not being clear enough?)

50
00:03:37,759 --> 00:03:39,560
(I have chosen you.)

51
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:41,360
(I will marry no one else.)

52
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:44,759
(Zhaohua.)

53
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,599
(I'm a Prince of a forsaken palace.)

54
00:03:46,599 --> 00:03:48,319
(I have no future.)

55
00:03:48,319 --> 00:03:50,319
(You are General Rong's sister.)

56
00:03:50,319 --> 00:03:52,360
(The Rong family's merits
are legendary.)

57
00:03:53,120 --> 00:03:54,120
(Your brother)

58
00:03:55,199 --> 00:03:56,360
(and my father,)

59
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:59,400
(how could they ever allow us
to be together?)

60
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:02,280
(Who says you're a Prince
of a forsaken palace?)

61
00:04:02,280 --> 00:04:04,000
(The man I've chosen)

62
00:04:04,000 --> 00:04:06,159
(will one day be the king
of this world.)

63
00:04:09,759 --> 00:04:11,639
(You are a commander trapped
in the corner of the board.)

64
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:14,280
(And my Rong family's
hundred thousand Xuanjia troops)

65
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:17,879
(are the chariots
that will break you free.)

66
00:04:24,920 --> 00:04:25,720
Yes.

67
00:04:26,839 --> 00:04:29,160
Your place in my heart

68
00:04:29,720 --> 00:04:31,439
can never be replaced.

69
00:04:48,319 --> 00:04:50,639
(He had a high fever all night.)

70
00:04:51,079 --> 00:04:53,480
(We'll have to try the Zhao Tribe's
herbal bath remedy.)

71
00:05:13,879 --> 00:05:14,879
(It's working.)

72
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,720
(Next,)

73
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:19,240
(he needs a full-body soak.)

74
00:05:28,639 --> 00:05:29,800
What are you doing?

75
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,720
You exhausted yourself

76
00:05:35,720 --> 00:05:37,560
to save me.

77
00:05:38,199 --> 00:05:40,240
Naturally, I want

78
00:05:40,240 --> 00:05:41,920
to take good care of you.

79
00:05:45,519 --> 00:05:46,759
You're healing me.

80
00:05:48,120 --> 00:05:49,079
How boring.

81
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,079
You saw through it so quickly.

82
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,720
You can speak now.

83
00:05:52,720 --> 00:05:53,639
That means you're better.

84
00:05:54,519 --> 00:05:55,839
Finally, I can sleep.

85
00:05:56,680 --> 00:05:57,639
My Lord,

86
00:05:57,879 --> 00:05:59,040
rest well.

87
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,439
(As expected, after midnight,)

88
00:06:02,439 --> 00:06:04,519
(security at General Rong's manor
loosened.)

89
00:06:11,399 --> 00:06:12,800
(She is...)

90
00:06:58,439 --> 00:07:00,160
Rong Zhaohua.

91
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:19,079
You've painted so carefully, General.

92
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,240
Does it look like her?

93
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:22,800
Seven parts the features,

94
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:25,519
eight parts the spirit.

95
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:28,360
If we add this vermilion dot here,

96
00:07:34,639 --> 00:07:36,079
you will truly be Zhaohua.

97
00:07:36,759 --> 00:07:37,959
(So it wasn't her.)

98
00:07:43,399 --> 00:07:44,279
Zhaohua.

99
00:07:50,959 --> 00:07:51,920
Who's there?

100
00:07:52,279 --> 00:07:53,199
Intruder!

101
00:08:03,560 --> 00:08:04,480
Catch the intruder!

102
00:08:04,839 --> 00:08:05,839
How dare you

103
00:08:05,839 --> 00:08:07,360
break into the general's manor!

104
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:12,439
(I've used too much Divine Power tonight.)

105
00:08:12,439 --> 00:08:13,600
(It's nearly depleted.)

106
00:08:28,399 --> 00:08:29,240
My Lord.

107
00:08:29,800 --> 00:08:30,680
Don't speak.

108
00:08:57,759 --> 00:08:59,279
Since you've delivered yourself to me,

109
00:08:59,559 --> 00:09:01,840
I won't let the opportunity slip.

110
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:07,200
Easy now.

111
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:13,559
My Lord!

112
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:14,480
My...

113
00:09:15,679 --> 00:09:16,240
My Lord!

114
00:09:16,639 --> 00:09:18,080
How did you get so badly wounded?

115
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:19,360
What is it?

116
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,480
It's Rong Xiu.

117
00:09:20,799 --> 00:09:21,720
He's brought men

118
00:09:21,919 --> 00:09:22,919
and is waiting outside.

119
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,679
He came fast.

120
00:09:28,919 --> 00:09:30,320
Hold him off for me.

121
00:09:30,320 --> 00:09:31,720
I'll change in the back
and be right out.

122
00:09:31,720 --> 00:09:32,279
Yes.

123
00:09:39,879 --> 00:09:40,639
My Lord!

124
00:09:44,200 --> 00:09:44,679
Out of my way.

125
00:09:44,679 --> 00:09:45,639
This is the Nanfeng Pavilion.

126
00:09:45,639 --> 00:09:46,960
You can't just barge in here.

127
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:48,919
A mere lackey of Feng Ye

128
00:09:49,320 --> 00:09:50,799
dares to block my path?

129
00:09:50,799 --> 00:09:51,360
You...

130
00:09:52,960 --> 00:09:53,840
What about me?

131
00:09:54,180 --> 00:09:55,480
(Nanfeng Pavilion)

132
00:09:55,480 --> 00:09:57,879
General Rong visits
the Nanfeng Pavilion today

133
00:09:58,039 --> 00:10:00,000
with such force.

134
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:02,759
Are you planning
to tear this place down?

135
00:10:04,919 --> 00:10:06,279
My Lord, you flatter me.

136
00:10:06,879 --> 00:10:09,039
I received intelligence

137
00:10:09,039 --> 00:10:11,200
that a foreign spy
has infiltrated the city.

138
00:10:11,919 --> 00:10:13,559
I crossed swords with him last night

139
00:10:13,559 --> 00:10:15,039
and wounded him with an arrow.

140
00:10:15,519 --> 00:10:16,879
I believe this spy

141
00:10:17,559 --> 00:10:19,600
is hiding here in the Nanfeng Pavilion.

142
00:10:20,480 --> 00:10:21,759
That's why I came.

143
00:10:21,759 --> 00:10:23,480
With just your word,

144
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:26,240
you think you can barge
into my pavilion?

145
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:27,279
How am I supposed

146
00:10:27,279 --> 00:10:29,080
to maintain my standing in Kun?

147
00:10:30,960 --> 00:10:32,799
When I crossed swords
with him last night,

148
00:10:32,799 --> 00:10:34,519
I noticed his build

149
00:10:34,519 --> 00:10:37,000
was rather similar to yours.

150
00:10:37,000 --> 00:10:38,320
When one is determined

151
00:10:38,919 --> 00:10:40,039
to accuse,

152
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:41,559
there's always a reason.

153
00:10:41,799 --> 00:10:42,519
As long as I'm here,

154
00:10:42,519 --> 00:10:44,519
you won't set foot in this pavilion.

155
00:10:44,879 --> 00:10:47,320
Then I'll use this spy's blood

156
00:10:48,000 --> 00:10:50,080
to justify this accusation.

157
00:11:13,780 --> 00:11:15,180
♪The moon sinks in the west♪

158
00:11:15,660 --> 00:11:17,100
♪The cold lamp burns low♪

159
00:11:17,300 --> 00:11:20,420
♪No one knocks upon
the mountain gate♪

160
00:11:20,740 --> 00:11:24,540
♪Snow-white winds and moonlight
touch me first♪

161
00:11:27,500 --> 00:11:29,220
♪Pear blossoms fill the courtyard♪

162
00:11:29,220 --> 00:11:30,740
♪Yet love and hate entwine♪

163
00:11:31,100 --> 00:11:34,500
♪Bound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desires♪

164
00:11:34,500 --> 00:11:38,500
♪Gathering red beans
for half a lifetime♪

165
00:11:39,660 --> 00:11:42,820
♪The Buddha speaks of countless paths♪

166
00:11:42,820 --> 00:11:46,380
♪How can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soul♪

167
00:11:46,380 --> 00:11:48,700
♪Trapped within
the space between your brows♪

168
00:11:48,700 --> 00:11:52,900
♪Falling deeper and deeper♪

169
00:11:53,340 --> 00:11:54,980
♪The green lamp sheds no light♪

170
00:11:54,980 --> 00:11:56,500
♪Upon one who entered the path♪

171
00:11:56,500 --> 00:11:59,700
♪The six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the past♪

172
00:12:00,100 --> 00:12:02,020
♪In dreams, it's you♪

173
00:12:02,020 --> 00:12:03,420
♪Beyond dreams, no one♪

174
00:12:03,420 --> 00:12:06,740
♪Clinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of suffering♪

175
00:12:06,740 --> 00:12:10,140
♪I can't forget the stars in your eyes♪

176
00:12:10,140 --> 00:12:13,700
♪Our fate had already taken root♪

177
00:12:13,700 --> 00:12:16,940
♪In this mortal world, there is only us♪

178
00:12:16,940 --> 00:12:20,380
♪Hopelessly bound by love♪
